node_7.subject: Isabella Rodriguez
node_7.description: This is Isabella Rodriguez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 6:00 am, travel to Hobbs Cafe at 7:00 am, open up shop at 8:00 am, greet customers and work at the counter until 8 pm, buy party materials for the Valentine's Day party at the cafe from 9:00 am to 10:00 am, have lunch at 12:00 pm, take a short nap from 2 to 4 pm, plan the Valentine's Day Party in the afternoon.
